folder: Tremont Avenue (East & Monterey Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
East Tremont Ave., east from Monterey Ave., showing part of the former Bronx Borough Hall Park and the Bergen Building, at the S.E. corner of Arthur Ave. Also shown is a panoramic view in a northeasterly direction as seen from the Consolidated Edison Company Building at the N.E. corner of Monterey and East Tremont Aves. May 1926.
Brown Brothers.

folder: Tremont Avenue (East & Monterey Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:

1926.
Brown Brothers.
